[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0850","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0850.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1005","title":"Novell GroupWise GWWEB.EXE 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Novell GroupWise 邮件系统的 Web 服务器组件 GWWEB.EXE 存在目录遍历漏洞。由于对 HELP 参数输入过滤不严，远程攻击者无需身份认证，可通过包含 `..`（点点）序列的特制 HTTP 请求绕过路径限制，读取服务器上任意 .htm 扩展名的文件，造成敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 GroupWise 5.2 及 5.5 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1005"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.380","remediation":"升级 Novell GroupWise 至 5.5 Enhancement Pack 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。临时缓解措施：在 Web 服务器（如 Apache 或 Netscape Enterprise Server）上通过 ACL 限制对 GWWEB.EXE 的访问，或删除该 CGI 文件。若无需 Web 邮件功能，建议禁用整个 CGI-BIN/GW5 目录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94571433731824&w=2","http://www.osvdb.org/3413","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/879","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19682","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1005.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1005","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1005.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1005.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1005.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wjwc-hc6j-xvf2/GHSA-wjwc-hc6j-xvf2.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/LubyRuffy/plugins/blob/f873b19f27c95eaf2993ca4acde5cb7965d2ee3f/pre2008/groupwise_web_interface_help_hole.nasl","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1005.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0850.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0852","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0852.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1006","title":"Novell GroupWise Web服务器路径遍历漏洞","description":"Novell Groupwise 的 Web 服务器组件 GWWEB.EXE 存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 HELP 参数提交特制的路径遍历请求，导致服务器返回文件系统路径信息，从而泄露 Web 服务器的真实安装目录路径。该漏洞可被用于后续攻击步骤的信息收集阶段，帮助攻击者进一步探测目标系统，扩大攻击面。受影响版本为 Novell Groupwise 5.5 及可能更早版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1006"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.503","remediation":"升级 Novell GroupWise 至 6.0 及以上版本，该版本已修复 GWWEB.EXE 路径泄露问题。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器配置中移除或禁用 GWWEB.EXE 的 CGI 映射，并限制对 /cgi-bin/GW5/GWWEB.EXE 的访问权限以降低暴露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94571433731824&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1006.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1006","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1006.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1006.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1006.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j6r8-2wq6-f58q/GHSA-j6r8-2wq6-f58q.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/groupwise_web_interface_help_hole.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88366/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1006.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0852.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0826","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0826.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0994","title":"Microsoft Windows NT SYSKEY 密码哈希加密密钥流重用漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统中 SYSKEY 机制存在密钥流重用漏洞。SYSKEY 用于加密 SAM 数据库中的密码哈希，但由于其在加密过程中重复使用相同的密钥流，攻击者可通过分析多个加密后的密码哈希值，利用密钥流重用特性还原出明文密码。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及更早版本，本地攻击者需具备系统访问权限，可通过暴力破解或差分分析手段获取用户凭据，导致系统账户安全受到威胁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0994"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.960","remediation":"该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及更早版本且无官方补丁。建议立即升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本操作系统，并启用 Kerberos 认证替代 NTLM；对于仍在使用 NT 的环境，应使用 SYSKEY 的增强模式（Syskey.exe /E）强制使用密码保护，并在注册表 `HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Lsa` 中设置 `NoLMHash=1` 禁用 LM Hash 存储以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ248183","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/873","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-056","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0994.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0994.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0994","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0994.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0994.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0994.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r7rj-gr4g-8x94/GHSA-r7rj-gr4g-8x94.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0994.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0826.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0830","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0830.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0998","title":"思科缓存引擎缓存内容替换漏洞","description":"思科缓存引擎（Cisco Cache Engine）存在缓存内容替换漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向缓存引擎发送恶意请求，替换或污染缓存中的合法内容，导致后续用户访问时被重定向至恶意资源或获取被篡改的数据。该漏洞源于缓存引擎对内容更新缺乏充分的访问控制与校验机制，影响使用思科缓存引擎的网络环境。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0998"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.483","remediation":"将 Cisco Cache Engine 软件升级至版本 3.2.1 或更高版本，该版本修复了缓存内容替换漏洞。若无法升级，可在网络边界配置 ACL，限制仅信任源访问 Cache Engine 的管理接口（TCP 80）和代理端口（TCP 3128/8080），并禁用不必要的远程管理功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0998","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0998.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0998.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0998","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0998.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0998.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0998.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0998.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87024/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0830.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0833","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0833.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1000","title":"Cisco Cache Engine Web管理界面信息泄露漏洞","description":"Cisco Cache Engine 的 Web 管理界面存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可直接访问性能统计页面，获取系统运行状态、网络流量、缓存命中率及客户端连接等敏感信息。该漏洞影响 Cisco Cache Engine 系列设备，攻击者可利用泄露的数据分析网络拓扑与流量模式，为后续攻击收集情报，需通过访问控制限制管理接口的访问范围。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1000"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.750","remediation":"在 Cache Engine 上配置访问控制列表 (ACL)，仅允许特定管理 IP 访问 Web 管理界面（如 `access-list 10 permit 192.168.0.0 0.0.0.255` 后在 HTTP 配置中引用）。建议将管理口绑定到独立 management VLAN，避免与业务网络互通。如无需远程 Web 管理，在 CLI 下执行 `no ip http server` 关闭 HTTP 服务。由于 Cisco Cache Engine 已全面停产停服，建议迁移至 Cisco WAAS 或等效替代产品以获得持续安全支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-1000","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1000.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1000.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1000","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1000.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1000.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1000.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6xm7-wpgr-j445/GHSA-6xm7-wpgr-j445.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1000.json","https://github.com/GiovanniMenon/llm4cve/blob/3ca85b2ae823c06810c546f320c2cd2f2707043f/README.md","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87010/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0833.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0833.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0837","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0837.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1001","title":"Cisco 缓存引擎访问验证漏洞","description":"思科缓存引擎存在访问验证缺陷，远程攻击者可通过提交空用户名和密码绕过身份认证机制，未经授权访问系统管理接口或敏感配置信息。该漏洞影响早期版本的 Cisco Cache Engine 设备，攻击者无需任何凭证即可利用此漏洞，导致设备管理权限遭非法获取。CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低，建议升级到不受影响版本或配置访问控制列表加以缓解。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1001"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.860","remediation":"建议立即升级至 Cisco 替代产品（如 WAAS），该产品已修复空认证绕过漏洞。作为临时缓解措施，在边界防火墙上对缓存引擎管理端口（80/443）设置 ACL 限制仅允许受信管理 IP 访问，并启用 TACACS+ 或 RADIUS 强认证替代本地认证。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-1001","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1001.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1001.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1001","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1001.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1001.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1001.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1001.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87020/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/lgp171188/launchpad/blob/eafda459366f2c43246e9c4fa98b8c008434bb68/lib/lp/bugs/scripts/cveimport.py"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0837.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0847","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0847.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1004","title":"Symantec Norton AntiVirus NAV2000 POProxy POP服务器缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Norton AntiVirus 2000 (NAV2000) 附带的 POP3 代理服务器 POProxy 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。未经认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标 POP3 服务发送精心构造的超长 USER 命令，触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务崩溃或可能执行任意代码。该漏洞影响安装 NAV2000 的 Windows 系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等，需升级至不受影响版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1004"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.250","remediation":"立即安装 Symantec 为 NAV2000 发布的 POProxy 安全补丁（文档 ID: 6206f660a1f2516a882568660082c930），或升级到 Norton AntiVirus 2001 及以上版本。如暂时无法更新，可禁用 POP3 邮件扫描功能以关闭 POProxy 服务，或在防火墙中限制对 TCP 110 端口的非信任来源访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://service1.symantec.com/SUPPORT/nav.nsf/df0a595864594c86852567ac0063608c/6206f660a1f2516a882568660082c930?OpenDocument&Highlight=0%2Cpoproxy","http://www.osvdb.org/6267","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/38970","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/39194","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1004.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1004","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1004.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1004.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1004.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4gvq-7hq9-g637/GHSA-4gvq-7hq9-g637.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1004.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000944.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0847.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1680","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1680.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0995","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 LSA 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 本地安全机构子系统（LSA）中的 LsaLookupSids 函数存在输入验证漏洞。远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的畸形安全标识符（SID）请求参数，触发该函数处理异常，导致 LSASS 进程崩溃，造成系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.8，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0995"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.080","remediation":"立即升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本操作系统（Windows NT 4.0 已于 2004 年终止支持，不再发布安全更新）。如暂时无法升级，可安装 MS00-006 安全公告中提供的补丁（KB249281），并在防火墙层面限制对 139/TCP 和 445/TCP 端口的未授权访问，同时禁用不需要的 LSASS 匿名 RPC 调用以降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ248185","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/875","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-057","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0995.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0995.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0995","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0995.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0995.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0995.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m7p3-89hq-9rch/GHSA-m7p3-89hq-9rch.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0995.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1680.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0734","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0734.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0934","title":"Greg Matthews Classifieds.cgi 命令注入漏洞","description":"Classifieds.cgi 1.0 存在 shell 元字符注入漏洞，远程攻击者通过在输入参数中插入 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等）可绕过程序限制，读取服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Greg Matthews 开发的 Classifieds.cgi 1.0 版本，攻击无需身份认证，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0934"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:21.560","remediation":"升级到 Classifieds.cgi 2.0 或更高版本，对用户输入的所有参数进行严格过滤，移除 shell 元字符（如 `;` `|` `&` `$` 等），或改用 Perl 的 `sysread`/`syswrite` 而非反引号调用系统命令。如该脚本已无人维护，建议替换为受支持的现代 Web 应用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/2020","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3102","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20444"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0734.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1314","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1314.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0935","title":"Greg Matthews Classifieds.cgi 1.0 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Classifieds.cgi 1.0 存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在 CGI 表单的隐藏变量中插入恶意命令，导致任意命令执行。该漏洞影响 Greg Matthews 开发的 Classifieds.cgi 1.0 版本，由于程序未对隐藏变量参数进行充分过滤，攻击者无需身份认证即可构造特制的 HTTP 请求触发该漏洞，从而实现远程命令执行，完全控制目标服务器。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0935"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:21.687","remediation":"该软件已停止维护，无官方补丁。建议立即从 Web 服务器移除 classifieds.cgi 脚本，或替换为现代且受支持的分类广告系统（如 OsClass 或 WordPress 分类插件）。如无法立即移除，可将脚本所在目录添加至 Apache 的 Deny from all 规则或 Nginx 的 deny all 配置以禁用访问。同时检查 Web 服务器日志排查是否已被利用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0935","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20442"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1314.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1314.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1314.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1681","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1681.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0996","title":"Infoseek Ultraseek GET请求缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Infoseek Ultraseek 2.1/3.1 for NT 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送超长 GET 请求触发该漏洞，导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 Infoseek Ultraseek 2.1 及 3.1 for Windows NT 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。无需身份认证即可远程利用，属于典型的基于栈的缓冲区溢出。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0996"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.210","remediation":"立即升级至 Infoseek Ultraseek 3.1 以上版本（如 4.x/5.x 系列），该漏洞在后续版本中已修复。由于 Infoseek 产品线已停止维护，建议迁移至现代搜索引擎解决方案（如 Elasticsearch、Apache Solr 等）。临时缓解措施可在反向代理或 Web 服务器层面限制 GET 请求长度，并对输入参数进行长度校验。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.eeye.com/html/Research/Advisories/AD19991215.html","http://www.osvdb.org/6490","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19679","https://github.com/CVE