2-ctr,aes128-ctr 限制加密算法。如无法升级，在 sshd_config 中显式设置 Ciphers !none 禁用无加密连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94519142415338&w=2","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1010.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1010.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1010","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1010.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1010.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wwmx-q2rq-7qgv/GHSA-wwmx-q2rq-7qgv.json","https://github.com/phx/cvescan/blob/d8d463e490d1d2d785179e8ace7ff59c2ea15f1f/README.md","https://github.com/privy-cafe/DollarLinuxClub/blob/57ae5d72b23dd6fe9fc5fca4dd120ffdf9dca123/misc/efnetretards.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1010.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0858.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0842","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0842.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1003","title":"Jgaa WarFTPd 1.70 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"War FTP Daemon (WarFTPd) 1.70 存在连接洪水拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 FTP 服务发送大量并发连接请求，耗尽服务器连接池与系统资源，导致 FTP 服务崩溃或无法响应正常用户请求。该漏洞影响 WarFTPd 1.70 版本，攻击条件简单，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1003"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-13T05:00:00.000","