DO VDOLive Player 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"VDO Live Player 3.0.2 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向用户发送特制的 .vdo 文件触发该漏洞，导致在受害者客户端上执行任意命令。攻击者只需诱导用户打开恶意构造的 .vdo 媒体文件即可完成利用，无需身份认证，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1007"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-13T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.627","remediation":"VDOLive Player 3.0.2 已停止维护且无官方安全补丁，建议立即卸载该软件，改用 VLC、Windows Media Player 等仍在受支持的媒体播放器。如需继续使用，可通过防火墙和组策略限制该程序对网络资源的访问权限，并避免打开来源不明的 .vdo 文件作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94512259331599&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/872","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19678","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1007.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1007","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1007.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1007.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1007.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-65cv-6848-4j95/GHSA-65cv-6848-4j95.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1007.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0854.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1668","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1668.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0993","title":"Microsoft Exchange 5.5 ACLs 访问控制漏洞","description":"Microsoft Exchange 5.5 存在访问控制漏洞，管理员对访问控制列表（ACL）的修改不会立即生效，需等待目录存储缓存刷新后才能应用。在此期间，系统实际运行的访问控制规则与预期配置不一致，可能导致已被修改权限的用户在缓存刷新前仍可访问本应受限的资源。攻击者可利用此时间窗口绕过访问控制策略，获取未授权访问权限，影响系统机密性与完整性。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0993"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-13T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.833","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Exchange 5.5 Post-SP3 安全更新（即 Exchange 5.5 SP3 之后发布的累积安全修补程序）。临时缓解措施：修改 ACL 后手动重启 Microsoft Exchange Directory Service（DS），或在注册表中调低目录存储缓存刷新间隔（HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\System\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\MSExchangeDS\\Parameters\\Cache Refresh Interval（秒））以加速生效。根本解决建议升级至受支持的 Exchange 2016/2019 版本，Exchange 5.5 已停止支持多年，不推荐继续使用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0993","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0993.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0993.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0993","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0993.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0993.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0993.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0993.json","h